        "Description": "Hello Agent.\rTonight You Will Be Infilitrating An Isolated Nightclub In Berlin.\rIn This Operation Your Targets Are Affiliated With A Cartel That Has Been Threatening The TC12 Millitary. Your Mission Is To Assassinate Them, In Order To Send A Message.\rWe Have Reason To Believe That The Cartel Has Some Association With The MK Corperation, So They Should Be Killed Quickly And Efficiently. \rGood Luck Agent.\r-TC12",
